#. <section class="sutta" id="an4.44"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an4.44:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 4"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 4"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an4.44:0.2"
msgid "5. Rohitassavagga"
msgstr "5. With Rohitassa"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "an4.44:0.3"
msgid "44. Dutiyakodhagarusutta"
msgstr "44. Valuing Anger (2nd)"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an4.44:1.1"
msgid "“Cattārome, bhikkhave, asaddhammā."
msgstr "“Mendicants, these four things oppose the true teaching."

msgctxt "an4.44:1.2"
msgid "Katame cattāro?"
msgstr "What four?"

msgctxt "an4.44:1.3"
msgid ""
"Kodhagarutā na saddhammagarutā, makkhagarutā na saddhammagarutā, lābhagarutā "
"na saddhammagarutā, sakkāragarutā na saddhammagarutā."
msgstr ""
"Valuing anger, denigration, material possessions, and honor rather than the "
"true teaching."

msgctxt "an4.44:1.4"
msgid "Ime kho, bhikkhave, cattāro asaddhammā."
msgstr "These are the four things that oppose the true teaching."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "an4.44:2.1"
msgid "Cattārome, bhikkhave, saddhammā."
msgstr "These four things are the true teaching."

msgctxt "an4.44:2.2"
msgid "Katame cattāro?"
msgstr "What four?"

msgctxt "an4.44:2.3"
msgid ""
"Saddhammagarutā na kodhagarutā, saddhammagarutā na makkhagarutā, "
"saddhammagarutā na lābhagarutā, saddhammagarutā na sakkāragarutā."
msgstr ""
"Valuing the true teaching rather than anger, denigration, material "
"possessions, and honor."

msgctxt "an4.44:2.4"
msgid "Ime kho, bhikkhave, cattāro saddhammāti."
msgstr "These are the four things that are the true teaching."

#. </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "an4.44:3.1"
msgid "Kodhamakkhagaru bhikkhu,"
msgstr "A mendicant who values anger and denigration,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an4.44:3.2"
msgid "lābhasakkāragāravo;"
msgstr "possessions and honor,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an4.44:3.3"
msgid "Sukhette pūtibījaṃva,"
msgstr "doesn’t grow in the true teaching,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an4.44:3.4"
msgid "saddhamme na virūhati."
msgstr "like a rotten seed in a good field."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "an4.44:4.1"
msgid "Ye ca saddhammagaruno,"
msgstr "But those who value the true teaching,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an4.44:4.2"
msgid "vihaṃsu viharanti ca;"
msgstr "who have lived it, and are living it now,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an4.44:4.3"
msgid "Te ve dhamme virūhanti,"
msgstr "these do grow in the teaching,"

#. <br>
#. VAR: snehānvayamivosadhā”ti → snehamanvāyamivosadhāti (bj, s1-3, km, pts1)
msgctxt "an4.44:4.4"
msgid "snehānvayamivosadhā”ti."
msgstr "like well-watered herbs.”"

#. </p></blockquote><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an4.44:4.5"
msgid "Catutthaṃ."
msgstr ""
